    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrowman lets you take on the role of a masked figure awakened with no memory, suddenly surrounded by a horde of monsters closing in, hungry for their next meal. Armed with only a bow you find nearby, you must fend off these relentless creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/e4725eb349cd184802a63530aadd6746.avif?t=1771511325\" width=640 height=206 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/8a960fccd1ef2ab90ccbbc121a3658c6.poster.avif?t=1771511325\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/8a960fccd1ef2ab90ccbbc121a3658c6.webm?t=1771511325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/8a960fccd1ef2ab90ccbbc121a3658c6.mp4?t=1771511325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your travels, you noticed that people seem to call you Arrowman – perhaps a hero of some sort? The strange powers you've discovered appear to be related to the masks you found, and you are quite certain that with time, you will be able to adjust these powers to your liking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/5b9aa21f979b8096f97396884be7e2cc.avif?t=1771511325\" width=640 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/e6506800a4d76079c5a874a3c6483995.poster.avif?t=1771511325\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/e6506800a4d76079c5a874a3c6483995.webm?t=1771511325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/e6506800a4d76079c5a874a3c6483995.mp4?t=1771511325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In here, people are now counting on you to save them from the monsters they call the Nightmares. Since there are a lot of them, the plan is to destroy their source. However, some of these monsters seem to recognize you - How do they know who you are, and what was your relationship?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/30ff990b082b487d30289779c65dee36.avif?t=1771511325\" width=640 height=210 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/b64b360ac413996328c61b1ca30365eb.poster.avif?t=1771511325\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/b64b360ac413996328c61b1ca30365eb.webm?t=1771511325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170690/extras/b64b360ac413996328c61b1ca30365eb.mp4?t=1771511325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a fast-paced 2D action-platformer with hand-crafted levels that guide you through a series of different environments. As you progress, you'll unlock new abilities to overcome obstacles, and your exploration will be rewarded with upgrades, allowing for customization of your powers. Each level challenges you to master different combinations of arrows, each with its own unique properties.</p>",
